luding demanding examples in stiff detonation simulation,\ndemonstrate the positivity-preserving, non-oscillatory and subcell resolution\nproperty of the present method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Jul 2020 22:37:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-14"}
