ively control three endoscopic tools which normally\nrequire two operators, leading to reduced manpower, less communication errors,\nand improved efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Jul 2020 07:05:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-14"}
